Blíží se!

70
00:05:11,380 --> 00:05:13,120
Musíme odsud vypadnout!

71
00:05:29,650 --> 00:05:31,130
Ta vůně zmizela...

72
00:05:42,500 --> 00:05:44,770
Jsi v pořádku, Saori?

73
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:49,740
To je...

74
00:06:08,870 --> 00:06:09,970
Saori...

75
00:06:12,970 --> 00:06:14,410
Ne...

